---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - The American Literacy Institute" description="Learn about The American Literacy Institute's history, mission, and commitment to promoting literacy across America.">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Us</h1>
      <p>Learn about our history, mission, and commitment to literacy</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>
          The American Literacy Institute was founded with a simple yet powerful vision:
          to ensure every American has access to quality literacy education. We recognize
          that literacy is not just about reading and writingâ€”it's about opening doors to
          opportunity, empowerment, and lifelong learning.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <ul class="values-list">
          <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Literacy education should be available to everyone, regardless of background or circumstance.</li>
          <li><strong>Excellence:</strong> We strive for the highest quality in all our programs and resources.</li>
          <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> We embrace new methods and technologies to enhance literacy instruction.</li>
          <li><strong>Community:</strong> We build strong partnerships with schools, libraries, and community organizations.</li>
          <li><strong>Empowerment:</strong> We believe literacy is the foundation for personal and community growth.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Our Impact</h2>
        <div class="stats-grid">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <h3>10,000+</h3>
            <p>Students Served Annually</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <h3>500+</h3>
            <p>Certified Instructors</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <h3>50</h3>
            <p>States Reached</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <h3>25+</h3>
            <p>Years of Service</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .page-header p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .content {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .content-section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    background-color: var(--white);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content-section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .values-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .values-list li {
    padding: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    background-color: var(--bg-color);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary-color);
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .values-list strong {
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .stat-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-color) 0%, var(--primary-color) 100%);
    color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .stat-card h3 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .content-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .stat-card h3 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
